&lt;ul data-path-to-node=&quot;4&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;4,0,0&quot;&gt;Formulate and execute the regional legal strategy aligned with overarching global business objectives&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;4,1,0&quot;&gt;Serve as the primary legal advisor to the APAC leadership team on high-stakes commercial ventures and regional expansions&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;4,2,0&quot;&gt;Oversee corporate governance regulatory compliance and government relations across all APAC markets&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;4,3,0&quot;&gt;Guide the regional team through complex multijurisdictional regulatory landscapes including data privacy and financial frameworks&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;4,4,0&quot;&gt;Manage disputes employment matters and corporate transactions within the region alongside external counsel&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;4,5,0&quot;&gt;Recruit mentor and develop a high-performing team of legal professionals across regional hubs&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot; data-path-to-node=&quot;5&quot;&gt;Experience and Qualifications&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-path-to-node=&quot;6&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;6,0,0&quot;&gt;Professionally qualified lawyer in Singapore or another major common law jurisdiction with exceptional academic credentials&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;6,1,0&quot;&gt;Minimum of twelve years of experience with significant time spent leading regional matters in-house&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
