&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;6,3,0&quot;&gt;Proven track record of managing distributed legal teams and navigating complex multijurisdictional challenges successfully&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
